{"tid":279690,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[連登有愛]想搵番一隻即食面 唔知香港有冇得賣","createTime":"2017-06-11T13:00:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-11T13:44:07.000Z","uid":119080,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9449351011fc27fcc81b45bcde155dd952e8c7bf","tid":279690,"uid":119080,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T13:00:15.000Z","msg":"呢隻即食面 D配料 味粉超好食<br />\n細細個係大陸食過一次就食唔停口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n叫做華豐三鮮伊面<br />\n<br />\n想問下巴打們知唔知香港仲有冇得賣<br />\n<br />\n之前係淘寶買仲有得郵運黎香港 而家唔知點解無得運<br />\n<br />\n問D淘寶賣家都話不發貨<br />\n<br />\n想問下你地知唔知邊到香港有得賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cbu01.alicdn.com/img/ibank/2016/026/408/2824804620_1844520870.220x220.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcbu01.alicdn.com%2Fimg%2Fibank%2F2016%2F026%2F408%2F2824804620_1844520870.220x220.jpg&h=b174f54c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://s2.boohee.cn/house/upload_food/2015/12/31/big_photo_url_ec2d8ffb5fc30e20c4a3cb65cc63aef5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs2.boohee.cn%2Fhouse%2Fupload_food%2F2015%2F12%2F31%2Fbig_photo_url_ec2d8ffb5fc30e20c4a3cb65cc63aef5.png&h=4867b2e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://g-search2.alicdn.com/bao/uploaded/i2/TB1G7G6MpXXXXbIXVXXXXXXXXXX_!!0-item_pic.jpg_240x240q50\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fg-search2.alicdn.com%2Fbao%2Fuploaded%2Fi2%2FTB1G7G6MpXXXXbIXVXXXXXXXXXX_%21%210-item_pic.jpg_240x240q50&h=7b077d6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://g-search4.alicdn.com/bao/uploaded/i2/TB1cZx8KFXXXXXIXpXXXXXXXXXX_!!0-item_pic.jpg_240x240q50\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fg-search4.alicdn